			// main content 
			.content-main
				h1 Stay compliant and avoid fines
				p
					| Once a business is formed, there is almost always additional paperwork, permits, or forms required to be filed. If this paperwork is not filed on time, a business can be fined and penalized. We can help your business complete this paperwork.
				h3 Business License Package
				p
					| As a business owner, you're responsible for making sure your business has the proper federal, state and local permits to operate legally.
				p
					| To make your job easier, we’ve partnered with BusinessLicenses.com, who can quickly and easily compile the permits, licenses, and tax registrations required for your business. (An additional fee of $74.99 will apply.). To learn more, 
					a#help_bizlic.help click here
					| .
				.form-group
					.form-fields
						input#bizlic_01(name='bizlic', type='checkbox')
						label(for='bizlic_01')
							strong Yes, I would like to get the business license package
				h3 California Statement of Information
				p
					| Within 90 days of forming your LLC, California requires that you file a Statement of Information with the Secretary of State, or pay a $250 penalty.
				p
					| Would you like LegalZoom to complete the Statement of Information and submit it directly to the Secretary of State? (An additional fee of $55 will apply.) To learn more, 
					a#help_casoi.help click here
					| .
				.form-group
					.form-fields
						input#casoi_01(name='casoi', type='checkbox')
						label(for='casoi_01')
							strong Yes, please help me file a Statement of Information
				h3 California Seller's Permit
				p
					| Most businesses that sell goods in California are required to obtain a Seller's Permit from the California State Board of Equalization.
				p
					| Would you like us to help obtain a California Seller's Permit for your business for $35? To learn more, 
					a#help_casp.help click here
					| .
				.form-group
					.form-fields
						input#casp_01(name='casp', type='checkbox')
						label(for='casp_01')
							strong Yes, please help me obtain a California Seller's Permit
